snippet.title: Lost Eidolons | Official Closed Beta 2 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re thrilled to officially confirm the Q3 2022 launch on both Xbox and Steam, and even more excited to announce the upcoming #ClosedBeta.

Register for Closed Beta 2: [https://bit.ly/3IfnRF7]
